thread.title: Dennis Harper-Davies

author: Dennis Harper-Davies
title: Dennis Harper-Davies
text:
Met at airport with chap with my name on a board, he carried our bags and took us to the car where I signed the paperwork. Nice car at a good price, we were given directions and went on our way.
No car problems during our stay.
Returned car to rental HQ with no fuss and transported to airport under 1.3 miles away.
Very good rental with a no fuss service. I recommend our car supplier, Venicia Car rental.
